{"tid":2154701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫管局員工陣線約見高層被拒 或發起工業行動","createTime":"2020-08-13T09:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T00:19:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":72,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"eefb77fbf16f2e47eb7828632e6d32226075b1f3","tid":2154701,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:31:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/7PZU4GUX7NBLBFH7NPLE2CMAEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2F7PZU4GUX7NBLBFH7NPLE2CMAEI%2F&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzlGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=e740a85f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2F7PZU4GUX7NBLBFH7NPLE2CMAEI%2F&h=d50f6d67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/7PZU4GUX7NBLBFH7NPLE2CMAEI/</a><br />\n<br />\n醫管局員工陣線就醫管局多項抗疫問題，早前要求約見管理層，多名成員今日下午親身前往醫管局總部大樓，但未有管理層現身。陣線批評醫管局在防疫問題有「四宗罪」，包括無視內地「核酸檢測隊」豁免註冊、及未有顧及員工憂慮，管理層拒絕會面反映局方無意解決問題，不排除日後再發起工業行動。"},{"pid":"a8a3bad56fd9b132944cb0caa20ffcff3428ab38","tid":2154701,"uid":173207,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:34:37.000Z","msg":"支持 政府又試開關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1979e24d15f40b51c9e700b0375c6fb9614eb3f2","tid":2154701,"uid":68111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66b788d08aba610216a6c8151d10eab768cb041","tid":2154701,"uid":68111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"推到上熱